Package: scoringTools
Type: Package
Title: Credit Scoring Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2020-08-26
Authors@R: c(person("Adrien", "Ehrhardt", email = "adrien.ehrhardt@centraliens-lille.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Adrien Ehrhardt <adrien.ehrhardt@centraliens-lille.org>
Description: Grouping essential tools for credit scoring. These statistical tools may be useful for other use-cases as well but were primarly designed for it. First, there are Reject Inference methods <arXiv:1903.10855>. Second, we build upon the already CRAN-available package "discretization" and "glmdisc" to automize discretization of continuous features, grouping of factor levels and introduction of pairwise interactions.
